Z","msg":"某巴西佬話2019香港地震"},{"pid":"32c443ddf08272d3fb1751bd946436f75b67ac33","tid":553363,"uid":48165,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"961b8efae461cacb7a4a985bda69949ba4c56afc","tid":553363,"uid":160807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d64be9c3518b1c0550132b542799ca4582c86f54","tid":553363,"uid":114704,"like":16,"dislike":8,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:24:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:26:36.000Z","msg":"冇記錯香港好一直有小地震wo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:31:42.000Z","msg":"如果咁講成個地球無一撻地方唔會，成個地表都由地殻形成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c271186b4f5d868f193fb360fd9ab906004acc","tid":553363,"uid":99028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:36:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ca8a7bf738a8b8aff179d3fc89f902ac463a230","tid":553363,"uid":4519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:39:46.000Z","msg":"香港的地殼結構<br />\n<br />\n世界大部分的強烈地震都發生於地殼板塊邊緣。香港位於歐亞板塊內，而並非處於板塊邊緣。著名的環太平洋地震帶位於歐亞及太平洋板塊的邊界並貫穿日本、台灣及菲律賓。香港距離這條活躍地震帶頗遠，發生大地震的機會很微。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n香港的地震風險<br />\n<br />\n根據土力工程處最新研究，烈度為V度（五度）或以上的復發週期約30至40年，烈度為VII度（七度）或以上的復發週期約500至600年。"},{"pid":"600742c28e8bd5d8d082d846b88d5f591f285a04","tid":553363,"uid":155568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e95dc0fcfca893ac1a908ed329fbc9a853dc9f9d","tid":553363,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:45:08.000Z","msg":"香港不嬲福地黎"},{"pid":"8557998d9093076bc774d4b933da2757ffcd9438","tid":553363,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a59b204529c6200a459df7fafc88d2a598bbc040","tid":553363,"uid":8478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:31:11.000Z","msg":"某巴西佬話2019香港地震"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:46:46.000Z","msg":"特首曾俊華 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3bf8b295db040a1a6000e5a508721218148e397","tid":553363,"uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港的地殼結構<br />\n<br />\n世界大部分的強烈地震都發生於地殼板塊邊緣。香港位於歐亞板塊內，而並非處於板塊邊緣。著名的環太平洋地震帶位於歐亞及太平洋板塊的邊界並貫穿日本、台灣及菲律賓。香港距離這條活躍地震帶頗遠，發生大地震的機會很微。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n香港的地震風險<br />\n<br />\n根據土力工程處最新研究，<span style=\"color: red;\">烈度為V度（五度）或以上的復發週期約30至40年</span>，烈度為VII度（七度）或以上的復發週期約500至600年。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係香港有機會有大地震啦"},{"pid":"514f9b5a2b441f62488b2fea8edd7c2aa820a697","tid":553363,"uid":69895,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e95dc0fcfca893ac1a908ed329fbc9a853dc9f9d","tid":553363,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:45:08.000Z","msg":"香港不嬲福地黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:49:54.000Z","msg":"但啲人閪呢～仆街"},{"pid":"b1a8fa30f3886c9187aae286b8c46da53c25e2af","tid":553363,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"514f9b5a2b441f62488b2fea8edd7c2aa820a697","tid":553363,"uid":69895,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e95dc0fcfca893ac1a908ed329fbc9a853dc9f9d","tid":553363,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:45:08.000Z","msg":"香港不嬲福地黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:49:54.000Z","msg":"但啲人閪呢～仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:57:06.000Z","msg":"地爛邊有人爭"},{"pid":"1052a1525d1ebc6a38c5d135e469bceebae57fb1","tid":553363,"uid":143260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6b2f56c00387158a8f9d0974bac4486f32e75d29","tid":553363,"uid":124126,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:30:33.000Z","msg":"由東平洲右上至左下，經過大圍到荔枝角，地底係斷層"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T11:57:48.000Z","msg":"其實幾十億年前香港有火山爆發同地震 個啲爆發就形成咗香港西貢的六角柱凝灰岩 (地質公園)個啲六角柱凝灰岩係全球嚟講係幾稀有，因為多數地方都係鹼性而係細柱(如英國)但香港係酸性所以